The '''2013 [[Malaysia National Basketball League]] Regular Season''' was the 33rd season of competition of the [[Malaysia National Basketball League]] (MNBL) since its establishment. A total of five teams competed in the league. The regular season began on 6 September 2013 with the 1st Series in [[Miri, Malaysia|Miri]], [[Sarawak]] and ended on 29 September 2013 in [[Kuala Lumpur]].

==Pre-Season==

A new format was announced for the regular season, where the teams will play in three Circuits. The playoff format was also changed: both the semifinals and the finals will be one-off series, instead of best-of-three series.

